{"lastModified":1772698410748,"uri":"c::7579684728::vessel::d5cbfb9f-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Gulet","Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Turkey, Bodrum\n\nThe luxury charter yacht, BLUE HEAVEN is one of the most elegant motor-sailing vessels to have been built in recent years.\n\nBLUE HEAVEN is well appointed, beautifully maintained and most importantly, has a top notch crew, who have spent many years honing their service skills. Friendly and attentive, this crew enjoys showing their guests the best that the area has to offer, be it Turkey.\n\nAt 30 metres, luxury yacht BLUE HEAVEN boasts a modern, alluring decor which offers a refreshing, minimalistic approach and is ultimately very restful… in keeping with the sublime beauty of the Turkish coast and the Greek islands. It is very easy to relax on board this luxury charter yacht, where indoor and outdoor areas flow seamlessly in a synergistic blend of ancient styling and modern creative flair: Designed in Turkey with a very roomy hull, BLUE HEAVEN’s design has allowed for a very comfortable and roomy interior… while also assuring a huge area of deck space. Life on board a luxury charter yacht in Greece or Turkey is then taken to a new level, with “al fresco” dining offering an ambiance which cannot be replicated elsewhere.\n\nBLUE HEAVEN offers masses of deck space with numerous dining and lounging areas — all perfectly proportioned, very comfortable and ideally suited to a style of luxury yacht charter that can only be experienced in Turkey or Greece - the most popular destinations in the Eastern Mediterranean.\n\nBelow decks, BLUE HEAVEN accommodates a party of up to 9 guests in 5 spacious and uniquely decorated cabins; two of which are amply-proportioned master cabins, two of which are twin cabins and one of which is a single. This luxurious charter yacht has it all: space, comfort, a caring crew and a full inventory of water sports and recreational equipment... all of which can cruise and sail at a pleasant pace through the scenic islands of the Aegean - in short, if you are considering which options are available for luxury yacht charter in Greece or Turkey - look no further than this serene beauty: a yacht which is beautiful under sail… and a quiet oasis when the Mediterranean sun is high and there’s nothing to do but laze on the shaded aft deck.","blueprint":{"name":"BLUE HEAVEN","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfb9f-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::9de695b0-3630-11f0-a937-9528fc22a07e/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfb9f-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::9de70ae0-3630-11f0-9c83-1bcb235df964/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfb9f-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::9de84360-3630-11f0-9ed1-c530d5a6142b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfb9f-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::9dd61af0-3630-11f0-bac6-51f3d8f034c3/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfb9f-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::9de954d0-3630-11f0-9ed1-c530d5a6142b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfb9f-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::9ddc0e60-3630-11f0-a937-9528fc22a07e/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfb9f-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::9de4e801-3630-11f0-a937-9528fc22a07e/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfb9f-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::9e37c2f0-3630-11f0-9647-41dedcbd00e8/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfb9f-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::9de731f0-3630-11f0-9ed1-c530d5a6142b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfb9f-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::9dd8b300-3630-11f0-bac6-51f3d8f034c3/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfb9f-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::9de6bcc0-3630-11f0-a937-9528fc22a07e/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfb9f-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::9dd75371-3630-11f0-bac6-51f3d8f034c3/{imageVariant}","/m