ompany and assistance as he has great communication skills and a very friendly personality."},{"name":"Hasan Inanc","role":"Captain","bio":"20-years-old Burak has an energetic personality, and it fits perfectly with his work position onboard BLUE HEAVEN. \n\nBesides being a great help to each of the crew members, keeping the yacht in the best condition, he is also responsible for water sports equipment."}],"pricing":{"weekPricingFrom":{"currency":"EUR","price":2041500,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":2041500,"unit":"WEEK"},"weekPricingTo":{"currency":"EUR","price":2741500,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":2741500,"unit":"WEEK"},"pricingInfo":[{"name":"May & October","effectiveDates":[{"from":"2026-05-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-05-31T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2026-10-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-10-31T23:59:59.999Z"}],"pricing":{"currency":"EUR","charterFee":2041500,"inputAmountTaxed":"EXCLUSIVE","note":"","unit":"WEEK","lineItems":[{"item":"Charter Fee","quantity":1,"unitPrice":2041500,"amount":2041500,"conditions":"Weekly","taxRate":{"label":"VAT","value":0.2}}],"total":2449800,"subTotal":2041500,"totalTax":408300},"inclusionZones":[{"label":"Greece","type":"Sovereign country","category":["Europe","Southern Europe","Greece"],"coordinates":[24.261736188816826,38.42232351533858],"bbox":[19.646484375,34.934472656249994,28.231835937500023,41.743798828124994]},{"label":"Turkey","type":"Sovereign country","category":["Asia","Western Asia","Turkey"],"coordinates":[35.10531997715448,39.093802942376584],"bbox":[25.6689453125,35.831445312499994,44.81718750000002,42.09326171875]}],"exclusionZones":[],"petsAllowed":false},{"name":"June & September","effectiveDates":[{"from":"2026-06-30T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-06-30T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2026-09-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-09-30T23:59:59.999Z"}],"pricing":{"currency":"EUR","charterFee":2479000,"inputAmountTaxed":"EXCLUSIVE","note":"","unit":"WEEK","lineItems":[{"item":"Charter Fee","quantity":1,"unitPrice":247